0.15
0.25
0.5
0.333







TipAnswer





c. \(P(X=3 \mid Y=1) = \frac{P(X=3, Y=1)}{P(Y=1)} = \frac{0.15}{0.05 + 0.10 + 0.15} = \frac{0.15}{0.30} = 0.5\).

